{"title":"变量","uid":"66ac6fe79dbb9aa78f5e1cf305b49e4a","slug":"变量","date":"2023-07-31T11:15:42.000Z","updated":"2023-07-31T12:40:27.615Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/变量.json","keywords":"serverDream's blog","cover":null,"content":"<h1 id=\"变量\"><a href=\"#变量\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"变量\"></a>变量</h1><h2 id=\"定义\"><a href=\"#定义\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"定义\"></a>定义</h2><p>变量定义就是告诉编译器在何处创建变量的存储，以及如何创建变量的存储。</p>\n<h2 id=\"变量类型\"><a href=\"#变量类型\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"变量类型\"></a>变量类型</h2><p>常用的变量类型有：int(<strong>4位整数</strong>)、double(<strong>浮点数</strong>)、long long(<strong>8位整数</strong>)、char(<strong>字符</strong>)、bool(<strong>布尔变量</strong>)。</p>\n<p>bool：存储<strong>true</strong>(真)和<strong>false</strong>(假)，是一个”开关”。</p>\n<p>定义变量的方式：</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-cpp\" data-language=\"cpp\"><code class=\"language-cpp\"><span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>变量类型<span class=\"token operator\">></span> <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>变量名称<span class=\"token operator\">></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<p>应用变量的方法:</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-cpp\" data-language=\"cpp\"><code class=\"language-cpp\"><span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>变量名称<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\t\t\t\t<span class=\"token comment\">//要先定义变量</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<h2 id=\"练习讲解\"><a href=\"#练习讲解\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"练习讲解\"></a>练习讲解</h2><h3 id=\"输入输出\"><a href=\"#输入输出\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"输入输出\"></a>输入输出</h3><h4 id=\"题目\"><a href=\"#题目\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"题目\"></a>题目</h4><p>小明买了一个复读机，不过刚买回来的复读机被小明的弟弟小昆给弄坏了，需要重新编写复读程序才能修好它。小明想让你帮他编写这个程序以修复复读机。</p>\n<h4 id=\"输入\"><a href=\"#输入\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"输入\"></a>输入</h4><p>一个整数n，表示要复读的数字</p>\n<h4 id=\"输出\"><a href=\"#输出\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"输出\"></a>输出</h4><p>输出整数n。</p>\n<h4 id=\"样例输入\"><a href=\"#样例输入\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"样例输入\"></a>样例输入</h4><pre class=\"line-numbers language-txt\" data-language=\"txt\"><code class=\"language-txt\">152<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<h4 id=\"样例输出\"><a href=\"#样例输出\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"样例输出\"></a>样例输出</h4><pre class=\"line-numbers language-txt\" data-language=\"txt\"><code class=\"language-txt\">152<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<h4 id=\"代码\"><a href=\"#代码\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"代码\"></a>代码</h4><pre class=\"line-numbers language-c++\" data-language=\"c++\"><code class=\"language-c++\">#include &lt;iostream&gt;\nusing namespace std;\nint main() &#123;\n    int n;\t\t\t\t\t\t&#x2F;&#x2F;定义变量n\n    cin &gt;&gt; n;\t\t\t\t\t&#x2F;&#x2F;读入变量n\n    cout &lt;&lt; n &lt;&lt; endl;\t\t\t&#x2F;&#x2F;复读(输出)变量n\n    return 0;\n&#125;<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<h2 id=\"课后作业\"><a href=\"#课后作业\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"课后作业\"></a>课后作业</h2><h3 id=\"A-B问题\"><a href=\"#A-B问题\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"A+B问题\"></a>A+B问题</h3><h4 id=\"题目背景\"><a href=\"#题目背景\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"题目背景\"></a>题目背景</h4><p>小A觉得他家的计算器太智能了，他输入1+1计算器居然输出了个3！小A想让你帮他设计个计算器来帮他计算（<del>顺便打一下他家的计算器的脸</del>）</p>\n<h4 id=\"题目描述\"><a href=\"#题目描述\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"题目描述\"></a>题目描述</h4><p>小A给你了a和b帮他算出a+b等于几。</p>\n<h4 id=\"输入格式\"><a href=\"#输入格式\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"输入格式\"></a>输入格式</h4><p>两个整数a和b。</p>\n<h4 id=\"输出格式\"><a href=\"#输出格式\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"输出格式\"></a>输出格式</h4><p>请你帮TA算出a+b的结果。</p>\n<h4 id=\"样例输入-1\"><a href=\"#样例输入-1\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"样例输入\"></a>样例输入</h4><pre class=\"line-numbers language-txt\" data-language=\"txt\"><code class=\"language-txt\">114 514<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<h4 id=\"样例输出-1\"><a href=\"#样例输出-1\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"样例输出\"></a>样例输出</h4><pre class=\"line-numbers language-txt\" data-language=\"txt\"><code class=\"language-txt\">628<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n","text":"变量定义变量定义就是告诉编译器在何处创建变量的存储，以及如何创建变量的存储。 变量类型常用的变量类型有：int(4位整数)、double(浮点数)、long long(8位整数)、char(字符)、bool(布尔变量)。 bool：存储true(真)和false(假)，是一个”开...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":712,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[],"tags":[{"name":"C++基础","slug":"C-基础","count":3,"path":"api/tags/C-基础.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%8F%98%E9%87%8F\"><span class=\"toc-text\">变量</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%AE%9A%E4%B9%89\"><span class=\"toc-text\">定义</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%8F%98%E9%87%8F%E7%B1%BB%E5%9E%8B\"><span class=\"toc-text\">变量类型</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E7%BB%83%E4%B9%A0%E8%AE%B2%E8%A7%A3\"><span class=\"toc-text\">练习讲解</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E8%BE%93%E5%85%A5%E8%BE%93%E5%87%BA\"><span class=\"toc-text\">输入输出</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-4\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E9%A2%98%E7%9B%AE\"><span class=\"toc-text\">题目</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-4\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E8%BE%93%E5%85%A5\"><span class=\"toc-text\">输入</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-4\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E8%BE%93%E5%87%BA\"><span class=\"toc-text\">输出</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-4\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E6%A0%B7%E4%BE%8B%E8%BE%93%E5%85%A5\"><span class=\"toc-text\">样例输入</span></a></l